Sintering array 600
3D printing gantry 1,200
Power management 500
Control and communications 300
Spares and consumables 500
Total 4,300

The delivered cost of this equipment at $c_T = 100,000 \text{ \$/kg}$ would be:

C_{\text{equipment}} = 4,300 \cdot 100,000 = 430 \times 10^6 \text{ \$}

Amortized over an assumed total constructed area of $A_{\text{total}} = 1,000 \text{ m²}$:

C_{\text{robotics}} = \frac{430 \times 10^6}{1,000} = 430,000 \text{ \$/m²}

5.4 Transport Cost for Imported Components

C_{\text{transport}} = m_{\text{import}} \cdot c_T = 65 \cdot 100,000 = 6,500,000 \text{ \$/m²}

5.5 Systems and Integration Cost

Additional imported systems beyond the basic pressure vessel are estimated at:

C_{\text{systems}} = 1,500,000 \text{ \$/m²}

5.6 Amortized Development Cost

Non-recurring engineering for habitat development is estimated at $500 \times 10^6 \text{ \$}$. Amortized over $1,000 \text{ m²}$:

C_{\text{amortized}} = \frac{500 \times 10^6}{1,000} = 500,000 \text{ \$/m²}

